Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:43.19,Cart_A_Tim,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\fad(688,0)\c&H5613DD&\bord1\blur0.7\3c&HF6F7F7&\pos(320,109.143)}Las seis personas que participarán son…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.98,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Hola.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.62,Gen_Italics,,0,0,0,,Soy Yuki Sumi.\NEstoy en primero de preparatoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.07,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Tiene un gran cuerpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.49,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Es perfecta de pies a cabeza.
